Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To Live Up to the Promise! \NDepartures of Their Own!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Late in the day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on which the Celestial Dragon's \Nship arrived at the Goa Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at a small village somewhere \Nin the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the person with \Nthe gigantic face today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've never seen someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the ship is huge, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,580... 581...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,582... 583...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,584...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Dragon! I got tired of waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, that's very bad!\N--Hey, treat him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching the ceremony \Nfor the Celestial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that without telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You attract too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My face, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to prepare as soon as \Npossible for what will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have enough food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave us some at the \Ntraining hall in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave here! Head back to Baltigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, in the Goa Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after the observers from the \NWorld Government left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes some junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are doing exactly the \Nsame thing they did before
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,accumulating another mountain of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! You're no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how strong you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's nothing if you can't hit a target!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubber is not useful in \Nfighting just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm telling you the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do is bounce back \Nattacks  and sink like a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making fun of the Gum-Gum \NFruit! I'll make you cry someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been creating new attacks \Nstronger than the pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, that was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm stretched farther than yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo! You're too easy on Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stronger than yesterday as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't you think so, Sabo?!\N--Don't you think so, Sabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo was a good brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You mean it'd be \Nbetter if I had died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meant it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo didn't hit me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What?! Be nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.69,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,I HEREBY ESTABLISH AN INDEPENDENT COUNTRY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby establish an independent country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.91,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ME TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:39.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ACE'S KINGDOM--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,LUFFY'S KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:47.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ACE'S KINGDOM    LUFFY'S KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to be strong enough \Nto live on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys belong to Dadan's Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me use your bath sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! You gotta help me! It's a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you wanted \Nto live on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, anybody there in Dadan's Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy got hurt! Please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magra! Please! Treat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, come in now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, it was no joking matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might have died if the \Ncut was a little bit deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three fought those beasts \Ntogether, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it doesn't prove that you're \Nstrong by fighting on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good enough at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makino came all the way bringing us sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to pay respect to other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm Luffy's brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's my job to go see the captain \Nof the Red-Haired Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who helped Luffy in order to thank him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Alright, I'll teach you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this would be the first one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we forgot to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you for the meal!\N--Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you brats! You got to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We did it!\N--We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear meat stew tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:59.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,7 YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:05.69,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ACE, 17 YEARS OLD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:12.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,LUFFY, 14 YEARS OLD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you, Luffy! I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! I'll be a lot stronger \Nwhen I leave here in 3 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wait! I'll make my name soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, the son of the King of the \NPirates, has grown up secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he quietly departed from \Nthe shore nearby Mt. Corvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! I wonder what Garp would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must raise him, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Whose baby is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh good. But I can see that \NGarp will be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was such an useless little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ace left a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He still has something to \Nsay to me even at the last minute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "Thank you for taking care of me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't do that! That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Boss, are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to wait 3 years more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I missed it by a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost got it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you keep the \Ncenter of gravity lower?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:42.16,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A FEW MONTHS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Ace made his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got his own ship and crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's great! Ace is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm gonna top him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,3 YEARS LATER - LUFFY, 17 YEARS OLD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving now. You're not gonna see me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor and Makino won't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the people in the Windmill \NVillage will be scared of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just go already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Then you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it - I feel awkward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan, I don't like mountain bandits...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I like you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense and go \Naway already, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why am I surrounded by such fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windmill Village at the edge of \NGoa Kingdom on the Dawn Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you take my \Nold fishing boat, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is gonna sink any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a small boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine! This is \Nwhat I wanna start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch over me! I'm gonna go out to sea now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo was first and Ace was second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm third but I'm gonna \Ntop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up with you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing screaming and mumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of incantation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not! It's a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who's Ace?\N--No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's finally leaving, \Nmayor. I'm gonna miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dishonor to the \Nvillage to become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nice day for setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes our local sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know who you're messing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this technique I've \Nbeen training for 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will learn ya, stupid fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He beat the sea monster \Nwith a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's become quite strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with finding a crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want at least 10 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the black flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy mourns the loss of his brother Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...weak!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Garp returns to Windmill Village, \NDadan greets him in outrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Luffy is lost in his grief \Nand helplessness after losing Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he watches Luffy writhe in despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei recalls the words of Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Want to See Them! Luffy's Mournful Cry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
